# Summary
This documentation describes the Refiner (Cohort) destination integration for Amplitude, which allows sending user cohorts from Amplitude to Refiner for targeted feedback collection. The setup requires API credentials from Refiner, mapping user IDs, and configuring sync settings for cohorts.

